  "text": "Biochemical analysis of individual mitochondrial respiratory chain complexes was performed on frozen cardiac muscle homogenates, as described previously [CITATION_1] . Specific enzyme activities were normalized to that of citrate synthase, a marker of mitochondrial mass.",
